show version	24\.4R1	cli.pdf Table 12 "Commonly Used Operational Mode Commands"内 "Software version ... show version"(L14066) + Change History表内 "24.4R1"実例(L16340)
show interfaces terse	Admin|Link	cli.pdf サンプル出力 "user@host> show interfaces ge-* terse" → "Interface  Admin Link Proto  Local  Remote"(L15947-15963)
